Title: Fix "Top alerters" dashlet site filter on "Site dashboard"
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1698668570
Edition: cee
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

If the "Site dashboard" was called from, e.g. the main dashboards dashlet "Site
overview", all sites were shown within the "Top alerters" dashlet.

The dashlet filters now for the correct site.
